    "text": [
        "Dear sir/madam,",
        "I am writing this letter to inform you that Recently, I received a letter regarding my car insurance premiums, which are going to increase from next month.",
        "Let me explain why insurance should not be up. First of all, I was holding my insurance with your company for the last five years. In addition to it, if you guys check my",
        "Record, I never had an accident and any other claim on my insurance. I understand that the prices rise over the few months, but increases in insurance, almost 20% is too much for me.",
        "I would recommend you that you should decrease my premium, how much is possible. Otherwise, I will go with another company, because they promise me to provide cheap insurance as well as an extra discount every year. I would appreciate it if you could consider my application as soon as possible.",
        "I am looking forward to hearing from you.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Gurjeet"
    ],
